Fig. 3 . Effects of tryptophan peptides on the fluorescence of bimane-labeled HscA. Emission spectra of bimane-labeled HscA(D422C) and HscA(A455C) in HKM buffer, 25 °C, were recorded following successive additions of Glu 98 –Cys 106 , W-97, or W-105 (0.9-274 μ m final concentrations); the uppermost spectrum for each sample was recorded prior to addition of peptide.

